Process called "parse_interpolated_string" takes parser as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Parse a string interpolation expression (f"text {expr}")
    Note: .
    Note: Parameters:
    Note:   parser - Pointer to ParserState
    Note: .
    Note: Returns:
